---
title: South Asian Shrimp Curry with Green Rice and Crispy Bacon
description: Crispy Indian-scented bacon is the perfect crumble for tonight's South Asian-inspired shrimp dish. Fluffy basmati rice will drink up all the velvety smooth coconut shrimp sauce!
